          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "According to a local news report by WREG, two cars were burglarized at two different stations. In one of those incidents, the thieves simply smashed the car windows and took what they wanted out of the interior. That’s obviously ",
